item.description:
Join  me for a few hours out on the trails for some fresh air and fun. We will be tossing discs( like frisbees) at baskets along the trail. You don't have to be good at it, just come and give it a try. There are discs at the store, where we will meet. The course is easy with 18 holes. Wear good shoes or boots as there may still be some snow. You will be walking into the tree area for your discs.. it does happen.  Also dress in layers and bring water. Thereis a nice sandwich counter at the store if anyone wants to eat after were done.

http://www.dgcoursereview.com/reviews.php?id=1588&mode=rev

  Questions or running late ? 603-315-0275 Cindy
